        </p>
        <p><a class="hover:text-white" href="team">The Team</a></p>
        <p><a class="hover:text-white" href="contact">Contact Us</a></p>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <div class="text-gray-200 pb-8 md:basis-1/5">
      <p class="uppercase md:pb-6 manrope-bold text-nowrap">connect with ifo</p>
      <a
        href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61577188505144&mibextid=ZbWKwL"
